Title: Signing Complete!
SigningMessage: You have signed the document. It will be securely stored on the Docusign, Inc. servers.
SandboxText: Get Started with the Docusign APIs Today
Description:
With the Docusign developer account, you can test our APIs for free!
Developer accounts do not expire and have Enterprise-level features enabled.

SigningCompleteEvent.Name: signing_complete
SigningCompleteEvent.Decription: The recipient has signed the document. It will be securely stored on the Docusign, Inc. servers.

DeclineEvent.Name: decline
DeclineEvent.Decription: The recipient declined to sign the document. This has VOIDED the document.

CancelEvent.Name: cancel
CancelEvent.Decription: The recipient has postponed signing. They clicked Finish Later instead of Decline to Sign.

ExceptionEvent.Name: exception
ExceptionEvent.Decription: An exception has occurred on the server during the signing session. Please check the parameters passed to the web service methods.

FaxPendingEvent.Name: fax_pending
FaxPendingEvent.Decription: The recipient has a fax pending.

TtlExpiredEvent.Name: ttl_expired
TtlExpiredEvent.Decription: The token was not used within the timeout period, or the token had been already accessed.

ViewingCompleteEvent.Name: viewing_complete
ViewingCompleteEvent.Decription: The recipient did not need to sign, but has completed the viewing ceremony.

SessionTimeoutEvent.Name: session_timeout
SessionTimeoutEvent.Decription: The recipient did not sign the document in time. The timeout is set to 20 minutes.
